
@startuml

' Define classes and their attributes/operations

class Player {
  +String name
  +int age
  +String position
  +Map<String, String> attributes
}

class DesignatedTargetProfile {
  +String targetPosition
  +Map<String, String> requiredAttributes
  +List<Player> longList
  +List<Player> shortList
}

class Scout {
  +String name
  +submitScoutingReport(Player, ScoutingReport)
  +assignScoutingAssignment(ScoutingAssignment)
}

class HeadCoach {
  +identifyDesignatedTargetProfile(DesignatedTargetProfile)
  +reviewScoutingResults()
  +decideShortList()
}

class HeadScout {
  +evaluateLongList()
  +setupScoutingAssignments()
  +reviewScoutingReports()
  +recommendPlayerForSigning(Player)
}

class Director {
  +makeOfficialOffer(Player)
}

class ScoutingAssignment {
  +Player player
  +Scout assignedScout
  +Date dateAssigned
  +Date dateCompleted
}

class ScoutingReport {
  +String pros
  +String cons
  +String recommendation
  +Scout scout
  +Player player
}

class RecommendationType {
  <<enumeration>>
  KEY_PLAYER
  FIRST_TEAM_PLAYER
  RESERVE_TEAM_PLAYER
  PROSPECTIVE_PLAYER
  NOT_A_GOOD_SIGNING
}

' Relationships

HeadCoach --> "1" DesignatedTargetProfile : identifies
DesignatedTargetProfile --> "many" Player : includes in long list
Scout --> "1" ScoutingAssignment : assigns
Scout --> "1" ScoutingReport : submits
ScoutingAssignment --> "1" Player : targets
ScoutingAssignment --> "1" Scout : assigned to
ScoutingReport --> "1" Player : about
ScoutingReport --> "1" Scout : by
ScoutingReport --> "1" RecommendationType : has

HeadScout --> "1" DesignatedTargetProfile : evaluates
HeadScout --> "1" ScoutingAssignment : may perform
HeadScout --> "1" Player : recommends for signing
Director --> "1" Player : makes offer

@enduml

---

### 📌 Notes:

- **Player** has attributes like position and a map of custom attributes (e.g., speed: high).
- **DesignatedTargetProfile** represents a scouting goal defined by the **HeadCoach**, including positions and desired attributes.
- **Scouts** submit **ScoutingReports**, which include a **Recommendation** from an enum type.
- The **HeadScout** evaluates reports and decides who moves to the **short list**.
- The **Director** only becomes involved once a player is recommended for signing.

